        Emergent geometry through quantum entanglement in Matrix theories
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Gray%2C+C">Cameron Gray</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Sahakian%2C+V">Vatche Sahakian</a>, 
      
