    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        The Calderón inverse problem for isotropic quasilinear conductivities
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=C%C3%A2rstea%2C+C+I">Cătălin I. Cârstea</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Feizmohammadi%2C+A">Ali Feizmohammadi</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Kian%2C+Y">Yavar Kian</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Krupchyk%2C+K">Katya Krupchyk</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Uhlmann%2C+G">Gunther Uhlmann</a>
      
