    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        The stochastic Gierer-Meinhardt system
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Hausenblas%2C+E">Erika Hausenblas</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Panda%2C+A+A">Akash Ashirbad Panda</a>
      
