        The Design, Construction, and Commissioning of the KATRIN Experiment
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="search-hit">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Aker%2C+M">M. Aker</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Altenm%C3%BCller%2C+K">K. Altenmüller</a>, 
      
