    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        A Strong Maximum Principle for the fractional Laplace equation with mixed boundary condition
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=L%C3%B3pez-Soriano%2C+R">Rafael López-Soriano</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Ortega%2C+A">Alejandro Ortega</a>
      
