    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        The Dirichlet-to-<span class="search-hit mathjax">Neumann</span> map, the boundary Laplacian, and Hörmander&#39;s rediscovered manuscript
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Girouard%2C+A">Alexandre Girouard</a>, 
      
