        Advanced Ore Mine Optimisation under Uncertainty Using Evolution
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="search-hit">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Reid%2C+W">William Reid</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Neumann%2C+A">Aneta Neumann</a>, 
      
