        In this paper, we investigate the impact of uncertainty in advanced ore mine optimisation. We consider Maptek&#39;s software system Evolution which optimizes extraction sequences based on evolutionary computation techniques and quantify the uncertainty of the obtained solutions with respect to the ore deposit based on predictions obtained by ensembles of neural networks. Furthermore, we investigate th&hellip;
        <a class="is-size-7" style="white-space: nowrap;" onclick="document.getElementById('2102.05235v1-abstract-full').style.display = 'inline'; document.getElementById('2102.05235v1-abstract-short').style.display = 'none';">&#9661; More</a>
