        <span>&nbsp;[<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2102.04178">pdf</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/ps/2102.04178">ps</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/format/2102.04178">other</a>]&nbsp;</span>
