        <span>&nbsp;[<a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2102.03713">pdf</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/ps/2102.03713">ps</a>, <a href="https://arxiv.org/format/2102.03713">other</a>]&nbsp;</span>
